### Crear un nuevo hallazgo

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hallazgos HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "El sensor no detecta la pieza correctamente",
  "line": "Linea 4",
  "partNumber": "123-ABC"
}


### 


### Obtener todos los hallazgos

GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/hallazgos HTTP/1.1
